ock, C., Lang, B., Rehm, L., (2000) SCOTSIM; An Evaluation of the Effectiveness of Two Truck Simulators for Professional Driver Training, Transport Research Laboratory, , Crowthorne, UK, Reference: PPR214; Robinson, B., (2007) Convenor Australian Association for the Study of Peak Oil and Gas, , Melbourne, Australia; (2001) Joint Science Academies' Statement: The Science of Climate Change (ASP ""The Work of the Intergovernmental Panel on Climate Change (IPCC) Represents the Consensus of the International Scientific Community on Climate Change Science""), , Royal Society May; Sparke, L.J., (2001) The Future of the Car in Australia: An Overview of Automotive Technology and its Role in the Environment, , Warren Centre Sustainable Transport Project, March, Melbourne, Australia; Tans, P., (2008) Trends in Atmospheric Carbon Dioxide - Mauna Loa, , National Oceanic and Atmospheric Administration, Hawaii, USA; Van Der Veer, J., (2007) Chief Executive of Royal Dutch Shell, Energy Community Leader of the World Economic Forum Energy Industry Partnership in 2007-2008, , http://www.shell.com/home/content/aboutshell-en/our_strategy/shell_global, Chair of the Energy Summit in Davos scenarios; Wright, J., (2007) Director of Energy Transformed Flagship, , CSIRO","Sparke, L.; Sparke Engineering, Melbourne, Australia; email: laurence.sparke@bigpond.com",,,,,,,,01433369,,IJVDD,,"English","Int J Veh Des",Article,Scopus,2-s2.0-77952136462
